Text: 'It was a nice trip from Mumbai to Goa by road. Pune Express highway then lonavala
  and one night at Lavasa. Beautiful weather and amazing journey. Next day from lavasa
  to goa...a inside drive thru forests where beautiful greenry welcomed like we r
  in heavens... Three days in goa.. The beaches, people, food all fantaboulous...fourth
  day back to mumbai ...

  Love it...'
